jsonrpc.parser

Class JSONFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsonrpc.parser.JSONFactory

  • public final class JSONFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Singleton class responsible for the creation of JSONObjects. This class also stores the current jsonrpc version and the standard json-rpc error codes.
